contentrichtext.text: '''Brookville''' may refer to any of the following: ==Cities and towns== * [[Brookville, Indiana]] * [[Brookville, Kansas]] * [[Brookville, New York]] * [[Brookville, Nova Scotia]] * [[Brookville, Ohio]] * [[Brookville, Pennsylvania]] * [[Brookeville, Maryland]] * [[Brookville, Ontario]] * the former name of [[Brooklyn, Tasmania]] ==Other uses== *The [[Brookville Locomotive Company]], manufacturer of railroad locomotives starting in 1918 *[[Brookville (band)]], a pop-band / solo-project of Andy Chase from the band Ivy {{disambig|geo}} {{DEFAULTSORT:Brookville}} [[Category:English toponyms]]
